{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"nonisolated","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"shadow","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"color","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Color","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore5ColorV","text":"Color","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" = Color(.sRGBLinear, white: 0, opacity: 0.33), ","kind":"text"},{"text":"radius","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:14CoreFoundation7CGFloatV","text":"CGFloat","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"x","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:14CoreFoundation7CGFloatV","text":"CGFloat","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" = 0, ","kind":"text"},{"text":"y","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:14CoreFoundation7CGFloatV","text":"CGFloat","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" = 0) -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"some","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/View","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore4ViewP","text":"View","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"\n","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"color","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The shadow’s color.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"name":"radius","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A measure of how much to blur the shadow. Larger values"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"result in more blur."}]}]},{"name":"x","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An amount to offset the shadow horizontally from the view."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"name":"y","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An amount to offset the shadow vertically from the view."}]}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Return Value","anchor":"return-value"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"A view that adds a shadow to this view.","type":"text"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Use this modifier to add a shadow of a specified color behind a view.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"You can offset the shadow from its view independently in the horizontal","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and vertical dimensions using the ","type":"text"},{"code":"x","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" and ","type":"text"},{"code":"y","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" parameters. You can also","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"blur the edges of the shadow using the ","type":"text"},{"code":"radius","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" parameter. Use a","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"radius of zero to create a sharp shadow. Larger radius values produce","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"softer shadows.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The example below creates a grid of boxes with varying offsets and blur."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Each box displays its radius and offset values for reference."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["struct Shadow: View {","    let steps = [0, 5, 10]","","    var body: some View {","        VStack(spacing: 50) {","            ForEach(steps, id: \\.self) { offset in","                HStack(spacing: 50) {","                    ForEach(steps, id: \\.self) { radius in","                        Color.blue","                            .shadow(","                                color: .primary,","                                radius: CGFloat(radius),","                                x: CGFloat(offset), y: CGFloat(offset))","                            .overlay {","                                VStack {","                                    Text(\"\\(radius)\")","                                    Text(\"(\\(offset), \\(offset))\")","                                }","                            }","                    }","                }","            }","        }","    }","}"]},{"inlineContent":[],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The example above uses "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Color\/primary"},{"type":"text","text":" as the color to make the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"shadow easy to see for the purpose of illustration. In practice,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"you might prefer something more subtle, like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Color\/gray-8j2b"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"If you don’t specify a color, the method uses a semi-transparent"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"black."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI","doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/TimelineView"]]},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/openswiftui\/timelineview\/shadow(color:radius:x:y:)"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"metadata":{"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"shadow"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"color"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Color","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore5ColorV"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"radius"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"CGFloa